text: i watched a thing on this the other day… it doesn’t really do anything apparently

So instead of just doing drugs, now we have to do the raw materials of drugs?
or things that are spelled similarly to raw materials

I wouldn’t snort it, but Sam and I put cacao in our smoothies in the morning. I’m a firm believer. The antioxidants are worth it alone. I also took part in a cacao ceremony in Guatemala. Pretty hokey, _but_ there were great vibes throughout the whole group. Felt like it was a placebo effect, but couldn’t validate one way or the other.
